#-           History§0
§0__________________§0
§0
§0Brandywine was§0
§0formed when four§0
§0members of Omnitopia§0
§0left to form a nation§0
§0that was more suitable§0
§0for themselves; a§0
§0place to call home.§0

#- These players§0
§0traveled the world of§0
§0Civex in search for§0
§0the perfect spot, when§0
§0they finally found the§0
§0perfect mountainside§0
§0taiga valley. From the§0
§0moment they first saw§0
§0the place, they knew it§0
§0could be turned into§0
§0their new home.§0

#- Although it was pretty in itself, those members had to§0
§0do a shit ton of terraforming to§0
§0make Brandywine§0
§0as pretty as it still is§0
§0today. Brandywine is§0
§0still growing each day,§0
§0and it's founding members are very proud of what it has become.
#- The sexy drunken hobbits love to party and are friends to everyone!§0
§0
§0
§0DISCLAIMER:§0
§0Some content in Brandywine is NOT suitable for children.
