#-           Laws &§0
§0           Such§0
§0-------------------§0
§01. We do NOT go into§0
§0conflict unless it is§0
§0self defence, and our§0
§0alliance with The Amani§0
§0Kingdom works the§0
§0same way because we§0
§0are bound to support§0
§0them if attacked.§0

#- 2. All houses must be§0
§0hobbit holes; nothing§0
§0above ground,§0
§0circular door, etc.§0
§0This information is also§0
§0on our subreddit§0
§0/r/brandywine.§0

#- 3. To use community§0
§0chests, you must§0
§0contribute to them.§0
§0Do not just take things and not give back. We have worked for those materials and will appreciate it.§0
§0
§0
§04. Don't be an§0
§0asshole.
